required_parameters.description:
At least two coordinates as start and endpoint of route, defined by longitude and latitude.
Required format: {longitude},{latitude};{longitude},{latitude}
Alternatively a polyline or polyline6 as input allowed.

api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://fast-routing.p.rapidapi.com/route/v1/driving/-74.0060152,40.7127281;-77.0501718249326,38.88933725"
querystring = {"continue_straight": "", "waypoints": "", "alternatives": "", "annotations": "", "geometries": "", "exclude": "", "bearings": "", "skip_waypoints": "", "snapping": "", "approaches": "", "overview": "", "radiuses": "", "steps": ""}

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "fast-routing.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers, params=querystring)
print(response.json())

